-- Chelsea Advances to Europa League Soccer Final Against Benfica
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2013-05-02T21:01:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-02/chelsea-advances-to-europa-league-soccer-final-against-benfica.html
Chelsea and Benfica both won 3-1 at
home to advance to the final of soccer’s Europa League.  Fernando Torres, Victor Moses and  David Luiz  scored as
Chelsea completed a 5-2 win over Basel in their two-match
semifinal. Oscar Cardozo scored twice as Benfica beat Fenerbahce
3-2 over two games.  The final of Europe’s second-tier club competition will be
played May 15 in Amsterdam.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  